In[43]:
# Top selling products

# Get category counts
category_counts = df['main_category'].value_counts()


# Plot
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 3))
ax = sns.barplot(x = category_counts.values, y=category_counts.index, hue=category_counts.index, palette="viridis", legend=False)

# Annotate bars with count values
for i, v in enumerate(category_counts.values):
    ax.text(v + 5, i, str(v), color='black', va='center', fontsize=12)

# Labels and title
plt.xlabel("Product Count", fontsize=12)
plt.ylabel("Products", fontsize=12)
plt.title("Top Selling Products", fontsize=14)
#plt.grid(axis="x", linestyle="--", alpha=0.7)

sns.despine()
# Show plot
plt.show()

# Highest Rating

rating_counts = df['rating'].value_counts().sort_index()  # Sort by rating value

# Plotting
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 5))
ax = sns.barplot(x=rating_counts.index, y=rating_counts.values, hue=rating_counts.index, palette='Blues', legend=False)

# Add data labels dynamically
for i, value in enumerate(rating_counts.values):
    ax.text(i, value + 5, str(value), ha='center', fontsize=10, color='black')

# Labels and title
plt.xlabel("Rating", fontweight='bold')
plt.ylabel("Count", fontweight='bold')
plt.title("Distribution of Ratings", fontweight='bold')

# Remove unnecessary spines for a clean look
sns.despine()

# Show the plot
plt.show()

In[57]:
top_3_Mcategory = total_percent_byMcategory.head(3)
middle_discount_Mcategory =  total_percent_byMcategory.iloc[3:6]
lower_discount_Mcategory = total_percent_byMcategory.iloc[6:]

def custom_autopct(pct , all_values):
    absolute = int(pct/100. *sum(all_values))
    return f'{absolute:.0f}%'

fig,axes = plt.subplots(1,3, figsize =(15,5)) #one row three column

axes[0].pie(top_3_Mcategory, labels = top_3_Mcategory.index , autopct = lambda pct : custom_autopct(pct,top_3_Mcategory),
             startangle = 140 , colors =['lightgreen', 'orange', 'purple'])
axes[0].set_title('top_3 Main Category By Discount')

axes[1].pie(middle_discount_Mcategory, labels = middle_discount_Mcategory.index , autopct = lambda pct : custom_autopct(pct,middle_discount_Mcategory),
